-- Brainsway Surges Most in Five Years on Depression Trial Results
-- B y   S h o s h a n n a   S o l o m o n
-- 2012-04-17T08:19:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-17/brainsway-surges-most-in-five-years-on-depression-trial-results.html
Brainsway Ltd. (BRIN)  surged the most in
more than five years after the maker of devices to treat
neurological disorders said trial results of its Deep TMS
treatment showed a significant drop in depression.  The  shares  gained 37 percent, the biggest intraday jump
since January 2007 when Bloomberg started tracking the data, to
27.65 shekels at 11:09 a.m. in Tel Aviv.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Shoshanna Solomon in Tel Aviv at 
